## NETLIFY DEPLOYMENT

- Each tool deploys as its own Netlify site
- No build step — raw HTML file, deploy via drag-and-drop or Netlify CLI
- No server-side code, no backend — all logic is client-side
- Sensitive config (API keys) should be injected at runtime via a modal prompt
  on first load and stored in `sessionStorage` — never hardcoded

